Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.22,0:00:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣下去他們兩個的潛意識
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(949,980)}Strelitzia
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,會透過鶴望蘭融合的!
